title: Calabash Ital Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan, Juice bar, Take-out, Caribbean, Jamaican, Ital
description: Vegan food restaurant, juice bar, and market. Offers ackee and gluten, curry chunks, a daily rotation of soup and vegetable dishes. Sells chunks and specialty food, supplements, personal care items, books and dvds. Previously at Ocho Rios market.
